cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper deals with analyzing images and identifying important individuals in them, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a measure of importance and investigates the correlation between importance and visual saliency, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of incorporating predicted importance in applications such as im2text, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
